  "frame_eqs": "dec_med = pow (0.8, 30/fps);\ndec_slow = pow (0.95, 30/fps);\n//dec_xlow = pow (0.999, 30/fps);\nbeat = max (max (bass, mid), treb);\navg = avg*dec_slow + beat*(1-dec_slow);\nis_beat = above(beat, .2+avg+peak) * above (time, t0+.2);\nt0 = is_beat*time + (1-is_beat)*t0;\npeak = is_beat * beat + (1-is_beat)*peak*dec_med;\nindex = (index + is_beat) %16;\nindex2 = (index2 + is_beat*bnot(index))%4;\n\nq22 = peak;\nq24 = is_beat;\nq26 = bass_att + mid_att + treb_att;\nvol = vol*dec_med + (1-dec_med)*q26;\nq27 = index + 1;\nq28 = index2 +1;\nq28 = 4+4*sin(time/13);\n\n\n//****tunnel viewpoint x,y\nvtrig = is_beat * bnot(index%4);\nvx = vx * bnot(vtrig) + vtrig * (rand(100)/100-.5);\nvy = vy * bnot(vtrig) + vtrig * (rand(100)/100-.5);\nvx = vx* below(index%15,7); //###\nvy = vy* below(index%15,7);\nq5 = vx*20;\nq6 = vy*20;\n\n//***tunnel width\nq21 = (1+sin(time/12))/16+.03;\n\n\n//****tunnel rotation\nrota = rota +.01*below(index%16,8)/fps*30;\nrota1 = rota1*dec_med + (1-dec_med)*rota;\nq7 = rota1/4;\n\n//****tunnel speed\nmovez = movez + .01/(.1+abs(vx)+abs(vy))/fps;\nq8 = movez * (q21*.01+1);\n//dyn. Aenderung von q21 bewirkt auch Richt.wechsel\n\n//***********************\ntrig1= q24*bnot(index%12);\ntrig2= q24*bnot((index+4)%12);\ntrig3= q24*bnot((index+8)%12);\ntrel = trel + vol/fps;\nz0 = 2/q21;\nhx = 4;\nhy = 4;\n\np1z = z0;\nq9 = 1*hx/(p1z);\nq10 = 0*hy/(p1z);\nq11 = p1z;\nq12 = .1+.02*q26*bnot((index+2)%3)*p1z*exp(-p1z/100);\n\np2z = z0;\nq13 = -.5*hx/(p2z);\nq14 = .87*hy/(p2z);\nq15 = p2z;\nq16 = .1+.02*q26*bnot((index+2)%3)*p2z*exp(-p2z/100);\n\n\np3z = z0;\nq17 = -.5*hx/(p3z);\nq18 = -.87*hy/(p3z);\nq19 = p3z;\nq20 = .1+.02*q26*bnot((index+2)%3)*p3z*exp(-p3z/100);\n\nzoom = 1.2 + sin(time/17)*.3;",
